**Story**
Once upon a time in a forest there live a monkey who lived on berry tree which was on the banks of a river 
in the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife .One day the corocide came to the banks of the river 
and rested under the tree . The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits . As the day passes
they became good freinds. But the crocdile'swife was greedy and she wanted to eat the monkey
